        <p>The Start Page is a handy window pane that displays when you first launch <MadCap:variable name="Other.Product" /> and remains open unless you close it. You can use the Start Page to open and create<MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Flare,Products.Lingo"> projects</MadCap:conditionalText><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Contributor"> files</MadCap:conditionalText><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Capture"> images</MadCap:conditionalText><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Mimic"> movies</MadCap:conditionalText>, view the online Help, and see news and updates. If you do not see it, select <b>View &gt; Start Page</b>.</p>
